text: Bolshezingereyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Nizhneulu-Yelginsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 188 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Yermekeyevo, 6 km from Nizhneulu-Yelga. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Bolshezingereyevo
